---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import AuthorCard from "@/components/author/AuthorAvatar.astro";
import AuthorAvatar from "@/components/author/AuthorAvatar.astro";
import { AUTHOR } from "@/data/author";
import { SITE_URL } from "@/data/config";

const description = "Tentang penulis dan arsip tulisan pribadi ini.";

const jsonLd = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "ProfilePage",
  mainEntity: {
    "@type": "Person",
    name: AUTHOR.name,
    description: AUTHOR.bioLong,
    url: SITE_URL,
  },
};
---

<Layout title="Tentang" description={description} jsonLd={jsonLd}>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[42rem] pb-8">
    <header class="mb-10">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-50 sm:text-3xl">
        Tentang
      </h1>
    </header>

<section class="rounded-lg border border-neutral-200/80 bg-neutral-50/50 p-5 dark:border-neutral-800/80 dark:bg-neutral-900/30 sm:p-6">
  <div class="flex items-center">
    <AuthorAvatar size="lg" />
  </div>
  <div class="mt-6 prose prose-neutral dark:prose-invert">
<p>Perkenalkan 👋, saya Fuji. Di internet biasa dipanggil waltahh, atau terserah mau manggil apa.</p>
  <p>Nah, untuk mengisi waktu luang, saya mencatat hal-hal yang menarik buat saya. Dan semoga juga menarik buat kamu.</p>
  <p>Sesukanya, semaunya, seadanya.</p>
  <p>Jikalau bermanfaat, alhamdulillah 🙂 Kalau tidak, tidak apa-apa.</p>
  </div>
</section>

    <p class="mt-8">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="inline-flex min-h-[44px] items-center text-sm text-neutral-600 underline-offset-2 hover:underline dark:text-neutral-400"
        data-astro-prefetch="hover"
      >
        ← Kembali ke artikel
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>